Ever wonder how to keep your teeth sparkly white? Join the UF College of Dentistry for a fun filled day of activities on fun ways to brush, floss, and maintain a beautiful smile. Plus, we will develop a strong sense of self, gain life skills and learn to seek challenges. All registered girls receive a dental goodie bag and an awesome Dental Health Fun Patch for your uniform.

$5/Girl Scout, $1/adult

** All attendees must be registered Girl Scouts for the 2016 Membership Year.  All adults must be registered and approved volunteers.

** A chaperone needs to remain onsite throughout the program.  Please see Safety Activity Checkpoints for the ratios.

** We are not able to accomodate tag-a-longs during this session
